and you don't remember?

26:16.700 --> 26:17.784
I don't remember.

26:19.995 --> 26:20.829
[sobbing]

26:27.544 --> 26:29.296
I'm so sorry.

26:34.009 --> 26:35.260
Judy would have stopped.

26:35.510 --> 26:38.013
