I said it? I don't remember.

26:38.096 --> 26:39.848
Okay. You need to leave my house
right now.

26:40.265 --> 26:41.391
Jesus fuck.

26:42.017 --> 26:44.352
-I'm a good guy, Jen.
-No, you're not a good guy.

26:44.436 --> 26:46.104
